        "created_at": "2025-12-06T01:02:58.498Z",
        "cooked": "<p>How many groups do you admin? From any one user‚Äôs profile you can quickly get to all the groups you are both in.</p>\n<p>I have a few folks in my life who change phones pretty often and it‚Äôs not really that complicated to go through all the chats I‚Äôm in with ‚ÄúNot Chris Old Number‚Äù and either remove them (if I‚Äôm an admin) or send a note to the group flagging that Chris changed their number.</p>\n<p>I would, however, love some kind of <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/warning.png?v=14\" title=\":warning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":warning:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"> flag that not everyone in the chat has even received this message. Or even just a <img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/images/emoji/apple/warning.png?v=14\" title=\":warning:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":warning:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"> flag that not everyone in this group is still using Signal.</p>",
